      'description' => 'Note that on August 18, 2020, a meeting was organized and held at the Serena Hotel in Dushanbe government officials and representatives of the private sector of Tajikistan and representatives of the company "GIOS" Republic of Korea in strict accordance with anti-epidemic requirements. Agency Director, Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of the Republic of Tajikistan to the Republic of Korea, representative of the Korean GIOS company and FAO representatives in the Republic of Tajikistan spoke about bilateral cooperation between the two countries and exchanged views on the production capabilities and exports of Tajikistan. At the meeting issues related to the production of products that meet export requirements were discussed, documentation, standardization, product safety, procedures and steps, and greenhouse conditions, refrigerators, shipping terminals, the volume and quality of exported agricultural products. Within the framework of the event, there were also bilateral meetings in the format "entrepreneur with entrepreneur" exhibition of export products. Note that following the meeting, a memorandum of understanding was signed between the Export Agency, the Korean company GIOS and the Association of Entrepreneurs of the Khatlon Region, and also by Mevai Kand.',
      'newsShowAllBtn' => 'Show all',
      'bgSize' => 'background-size: cover;'
